fields.name: Bridgestone TURANZA T005 TL 195/60 R15 88H
fields.description:
The Bridgestone Turanza T005 is a high performance summer tire, which is the successor of the well-known Bridgestone Turanza T001. The Turanza T005 is a summer tire that looks good among mid-range and upper-middle class passenger cars.

Developed and produced in Europe, the Bridgestone Turanza T005 delivers excellent performance on dry and wet surfaces, as well as being fuel efficient, making it the perfect all-round summer tyre.

Compared to the Turanza T001, the Bridgestone Turanza T005 provides much better traction on dry and wet surfaces and also has a lower rolling resistance.

Bridgestone summer tires are known for the various innovations incorporated into them . These innovations combine to provide the Bridgestone Turanza T005 with excellent driving performance and characteristics.

fields.name: Continental PremiumContact 2 175/65 R15 84H
fields.description:
The Continental PremiumContact 2 is the perfect summer tire for medium-sized and larger cars. This high-quality summer tire responds just as vigorously to wet roads as it does to dry roads. This means it offers you top safety and driving comfort under all circumstances. So it's no surprise that the tire scores very high (13th place) in the Tires top-100.

While driving you immediately notice how well Continental has thought about this tire. Braking, accelerating, cornering: the Continental PremiumContact 2 is all equally precise and smooth. In short, the tire delivers optimum performance. The long service life and favorable fuel consumption are also nice for your wallet. In summer you can hardly wish for a better tire.

fields.name: Dunlop SP Sport Fastresponse 205/55 R16 94H
fields.description:
The Dunlop SP Sport Fast Response is a superior summer tire for passenger cars with a distinctly sporty character. Its highly reliable handling and impressive performance come into its own on dry and wet roads. Under all circumstances you will experience a permanent feeling of comfort and safety. A great tire to have under your car!

This top-class tire is highly regarded for its exemplary agility and precise handling on the road. Its road holding is second to none, whether you're riding on wet or dry roads. This makes it an ideal and reliable summer tire for all conditions.

fields.name: Goodyear Eagle F1 Asymmetric 235/45 R18 94W
fields.description:
The Goodyear Eagle F1 Asymmetric 5 is a maximum performance summer tire that fits perfectly on mid-range and higher-end cars. The tire is characterized by its excellent braking performance and good handling characteristics. It ensures that you always have optimal control; both on wet and dry roads.

The technology for the new and reinforced construction of the Goodyear Eagle F1 Asymmetric (the Reinforced Construction technology) provides a stronger and lightweight composition. This improves cornering performance, handling, wear rate and fuel consumption, among other things. It also shortens braking distances on wet and dry roads.

fields.name: Goodyear Duragrip 175/65 R15 88T
fields.description:
The Goodyear Duragrip is a summer tire for passenger cars. It is a car tire that has been specially developed for durability. This means that it lasts considerably longer due to a special construction that reduces rolling resistance.

Due to the manufacturing process of the Goodyear Duragrip, the tire is labeled 'environmentally friendly'. Cleaner components have been used, which reduce CO2 emissions during both production and use.

Goodyear tires have been known for their safety for many years. Many car manufacturers recommend these tires and for some brands this tire is even the first installation.

The Goodyear Duragrip is the tire of choice for drivers of the Mazda 323, the Nissan Note, the Peugeot 206, the Peugeot 406 and the Renault Clio, among others. And maybe yours too?

fields.name: Pirelli W 190 Snowcontrol Se 205/55 R16 91T
fields.description:
The Pirelli Winter 190 SnowControl 3 is a winter tire for city and middle class cars. With this car tire you can safely hit the road during the winter months.

This Pirelli Winter 190 SnowControl 3 offers reliable road holding, great pulling power and pleasant braking performance in winter weather.

This tire is popular with owners of the Peugeot 207 and 208 and 306, the Ford Fiesta and the Citroën C3.

fields.name: Bridgestone Blizzak LM-32 205/55 R16 91H
fields.description:
The Bridgestone Blizzak LM 32 is the ultimate winter tire for almost all passenger cars, from small and compact models to the upper middle class. A tire to withstand the winter without any problems, even in the most extreme conditions. Not only does this tire perform excellently on snow and ice, but also in less harsh winter weather. It proves itself just as easily on wet as on dry roads.

The beautiful properties of the Bridgestone Blizzak LM 32 naturally result in safe and carefree driving throughout the winter. Its braking performance is unparalleled, its steering precision and stability unparalleled. In addition, the tire is also very durable and fuel-efficient, so it certainly won't affect your budget!

fields.name: Goodyear UltraGrip 8 205/55 R16 91H
fields.description:
The Goodyear UltraGrip 8 is a winter tire with many safe and comfortable driving characteristics. It is very suitable for compact and middle class passenger cars. In addition to great performance in all winter conditions, the tire also offers fuel-saving innovations that allow you to drive more economically and protect the environment. Thanks to the above-average performance of the tire, it is in a strong position in the Winter Tires Top-100.

Many good qualities come together in this tire. For example, the traction in snow is a particularly strong point of the Goodyear UltraGrip 8. This ensures a shorter braking distance on snow. In addition, these tires offer extra grip on winter roads and contribute to your safety and driving comfort on winter roads. Despite its convincing performance, this tire also proves to be remarkably durable. So you can use it longer before it needs to be replaced.

fields.name: Bridgestone Blizzak LM-30 175/65 R15 84T
fields.description:
The Bridgestone Blizzak LM 30 is a particularly safe winter tire for compact and medium-sized cars. With this first-class tire you can comfortably drive towards spring. Because the tire is stable, smoothly controllable and extremely reliable under all conditions. Of course in the snow and on icy roads, but also in the rain and on dry surfaces. Particularly striking is its great braking performance, but also a smooth steering precision. A tire that you can easily handle in winter.

This tire contains a lot of advanced technology. The manufacturer has done everything possible to set a new standard for winter tires with the Bridgestone Blizzak LM 30. The innovative rubber and well thought-out construction provide a balanced tire that you can rely on blindly. Your safety and driving comfort are paramount in all winter conditions.

fields.name: Hankook Kinergy eco2 (K435) 175/70 R14 84T
fields.description:
The Hankook Kinergy Eco 2 K435 is a summer tire that has been developed for modern small, compact and medium-sized vehicles. Like its predecessor, the Hankook Kinergy Eco K425, the Hankook Kinergy Eco 2 K435 has placed an emphasis on safety, fuel consumption and driving comfort.

The Kinergy Eco 2 is one of Hankook's most fuel-efficient tires, which also looks great on aluminum and steel rims. According to Hankook, this summer tire is the best choice for the driver and the environment.

The Hankook Kinergy Eco 2 K435 has been specially designed to save a lot of fuel and to guarantee the driver's driving comfort.

fields.name: Vredestein T-Trac 2 175/70 R14 84T
fields.description:
The Vredestein T-Trac 2 is a real all-rounder. A summer tire for your passenger car that has been specially designed for performance-oriented, safe and economical driving. This tire performs best at temperatures above 7 degrees Celsius.

The Vredestein T-Trac 2 is a tire with good value for money and a good choice for your middle class car. With this tire you drive safely and you save kilometer after kilometer on fuel. This also protects the environment.

The tire scores well with owners of, among others, the Suzuki Alto and the Ignis, the Renault Kangoo, the Peugeot Partner and the Peugeot 206. Drivers of these cars all have pleasant experiences with this tire.

First class grip on snowy, slushy and wet roads
Predictable and balanced driving experience
Smooth rolling saves fuel and preserves the environment
